Opening in June 2016. Hawkes Bay, New Zealand. The Battle Cave will have 10 state of the art custom built gaming computers. The best gaming chairs, headsets and other accessories. They will be in-store champions and monthly tournaments. Live streaming on youtube and twitch. 
A kiosk to keep you refreshed while you play. Great pricing. 
Come like our facebook page to get all the info as it unfolds. Guest appearance on opening night by {{champion:222}}
